projects.description:
This project is created in order to record and progress all the issues, suggestions and new proposals.

The respective GM's & DGM's need to register their sub core departments issue, suggestion or new proposal as Tasks and bring it to the discussion of the committee.

Further individual department can raise their issues as tickets in OTRS by mailing it to "cc.support@thechennaisilks.com". Those tickets will be created as tasks in this project and discussed during the meeting.
